	Honk-Kong</font></td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
	<td align="right"><font color="#800080" size="3"
	face="Arial">Power: </font></td>
	<td><font color="#000080" size="3" face="Arial">6 1,5v
	batteries (UM2 type), or 9v DC 200mA transformer</font></td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
	<td align="right"><font color="#800080" size="3"
	face="Arial">Games: </font></td>
	<td><font color="#000080" size="3" face="Arial">Cartridges
	PC-501 to PC-508</font></td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
	<td align="right"><font color="#800080" size="3"
	face="Arial">Controllers: </font></td>
	<td><font color="#000080" size="3" face="Arial">2
	detachable joysticks without return, and with a
	push-button for serving.</font></td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
	<td align="right"><font color="#800080" size="3"
	face="Arial">Scoring: </font></td>
	<td><font color="#000080" size="3" face="Arial">On screen</font></td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
	<td align="right"><font color="#800080" size="3"
	face="Arial">Video: </font></td>
	<td><font color="#000080" size="3" face="Arial">UHF
	Channel 36, SECAM 625-L color</font></td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
	<td align="right"><font color="#800080" size="3"
	face="Arial">Extension: </font></td>
	<td><font color="#000080" size="3" face="Arial">5 pins
	DIN plug on the left side for the gun/rifle</font></td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
